777
00:38:28,000 --> 00:38:29,100
What is this?

778
00:38:29,800 --> 00:38:31,100
lt's stuck again.

779
00:38:31,800 --> 00:38:35,600
lfthis was one of my stories,
this elevator would get stuck...

780
00:38:35,800 --> 00:38:39,300
and you and l would start a major
affair, and fall in love.

781
00:38:49,800 --> 00:38:52,200
Promise you won't
fall in love with me.

782
00:38:52,700 --> 00:38:53,500
No?

783
00:38:54,600 --> 00:38:56,900
Definitely not.
Not a good idea.

784
00:38:57,100 --> 00:38:57,900
Why?

785
00:38:58,300 --> 00:38:59,100
Because...

786
00:38:59,400 --> 00:39:01,100
l'm too screwed up.

787
00:39:02,800 --> 00:39:03,800
l have...

788
