too many quirks.

789
00:39:09,200 --> 00:39:11,400
l have trouble being faithful.

790
00:39:12,100 --> 00:39:14,700
l have too many phobias.
l'm crazy.

791
00:39:15,000 --> 00:39:17,600
Yeah, but l fell in love with you
before l met you.

792
00:39:18,300 --> 00:39:19,800
When l read you.

793
00:39:20,100 --> 00:39:22,200
