with my work.

794
00:39:22,800 --> 00:39:24,500
That's a different thing.

795
00:39:25,300 --> 00:39:28,500
l love yourwork.
l love your imagination.

796
00:39:29,000 --> 00:39:30,200
l love it.

797
00:39:30,500 --> 00:39:33,900
