You know what l mean.

798
00:39:34,400 --> 00:39:37,800
We're not characters
in a fictional thing.

799
00:39:39,000 --> 00:39:41,100
-So don't fall in love with me.
-Kiss me.

800
00:39:41,400 --> 00:39:43,900
-Promise you won't.
-No, kiss me.

801
00:39:44,900 --> 00:39:46,300
l promise.

802
00:40:01,400 --> 00:40:02,300
Thank you.

803
00:40:05,800 --> 00:40:08,100
The subway took forever. Sorry.

804
00:40:08,800 --> 00:40:10,700
You said you weren't coming.

805
00:40:11,000 --> 00:40:11,800
What do you mean?

806
00:40:12,000 --> 00:40:13,800
-We said 10. l'm sure.
-No.

807
00:40:14,000 --> 00:40:16,400
l called last night,
to say l got out of my thing.

808
00:40:16,700 --> 00:40:17,800
You called? When?

809
00:40:18,000 --> 00:40:20,300
At 9.30 last night.
You don't remember?

810
00:40:20,500 --> 00:40:22,000
l interrupted you writing.

811
00:40:22,200 --> 00:40:24,600
-We spoke on the phone.
-Absolutely.

812
00:40:25,000 --> 00:40:27,200
My mind has been playing tricks.

813
00:40:27,400 --> 00:40:29,100
This is Cookie Williams,
Richard.

814
00:40:29,400 --> 00:40:30,500
How ya doing?

815
00:40:30,700 --> 00:40:31,800
What's so special
about this honor?

816
00:40:32,000 --> 00:40:34,700
